    After &#60;span class=&#34;hljs-keyword&#34;&#62;this&#60;/span&#62; operation, &#60;span class=&#34;hljs-number&#34;&#62;7&#60;/span&#62;,&#60;span class=&#34;hljs-number&#34;&#62;538&#60;/span&#62; kB of additional disk space will be used.
