    Get:&#60;span class=&#34;hljs-number&#34;&#62;3&#60;/span&#62; http:&#60;span class=&#34;hljs-comment&#34;&#62;//mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ trusty/universe nodejs amd64 0.10.25~dfsg2-2ubuntu1 [684 kB]&#60;/span&#62;
